## Comandi

`{KEY}` = `{JIRA_KEY}-{num}`. Case-insensitive sulla key.

| Comando | Effetto |
| --- | --- |
| **`gogo {KEY}`** | FULL silent вЂ” START в†’ subtask в†’ ok chiudi automatico в†’ END-A |
| `procedi Story {KEY}` | Piano в†’ implementazione в†’ confirm |
| `chiudi Story {KEY}` | Push + PR + catalogo + gap test + parent Jira в†’ Fatto |
| **`chiudi fast Story {KEY}`** | Push + PR + catalogo + parent Jira (no gap test) |

Varianti: `FULL silent`, `chiudi fast`, `ok chiudi` вЂ” regole silenzio/output correlate.

