## Output chat (procedi / gogo)

| Fase | Contenuto |
| --- | --- |
| **START** | AC, DoD, STATO, BRANCH, subtask, Macrostep |
| **PROGRESS** | Tabella Macrostep |
| **END-A / END-B** | Template workflow |

Formato END вЂ” repo = **progetto istanziato**:

```text
PR: {url}
Jira: https://myfuturejobsearch.atlassian.net/browse/{KEY}
Repo: [{PRJ_GITHUB_REPO}](https://github.com/{owner}/{repo}) В· branch `{branch}` В· commit `{hash}`
```

`owner`/`repo` da `PRJ_GITHUB_OWNER` / `PRJ_GITHUB_REPO` dell'overlay attivo вЂ” **non** assumere sempre PortalAdmin.

